descriptionHTML:
Grand Bundle is a collection of a contrasting watch faces to enhance your options of customizing your smart watch. You can enjoy two different styles of watch faces each with dozens of custom features. Awesome built-in features include ambient mode of all the styles, weather information, Battery status, Humidity level, date and much more.
Frillroid is focused in creating professional looking watch faces. Each Watch Face is engineered by high quality design and required keen concentration to choose the watch colors with soothing effect which ultimately makes the watch unmatchable and incomparable.
Key custom features:-
• Latest Weather updates
• Classic Design
• Ultimate readability
• Clean and simplistic look
• Hi contrast and high colors
• Remaining battery life of your device so you exactly know when to charge
• Ambient mode engineered with the latest wear Api makes your watch’s battery stronger than ever
Grand Bundle is designed for rectangular and circular smart watches such as the LG G Watch, LG G Watch R, Samsung Gear Live, Motorola Moto 360, LG G Watch, LG G WATCH R, and Samsung Gear Live, Asus zenwatch and sony smartwatch 3.
